244
00:12:47,558 --> 00:12:48,858
Entendeu?

245
00:12:49,459 --> 00:12:50,759
Não.

246
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:54,112
Srta. Healy, 100 mil empregos
do governo dependem

247
00:12:54,113 --> 00:12:55,869
